data.description: Captivating four-bedroom, three-bathroom home with a spacious floor plan. Private backyard, complete with a small stream. The living room features vaulted ceilings and a cozy gas log fireplace. The kitchen awaits your culinary adventures with granite countertops and tilted backsplash. Relax in the large master suite featuring tray ceilings and a master bathroom with double vanities and a separate soaking tub. Oversized bonus room adjacent to the fourth bedroom, spacious laundry room, and two-car garage provide convenience. Enjoy the private back deck and fenced back yard. Community features a large common area and nature trails around the subdivision.
